| `src/services/*.service.ts` | `src/services/*.service.ts` (–±–µ–Ј –Є–Ј–Љ–µ–љ–µ–љ–Є–є) |
| `views/*.ejs` | `app/**/page.tsx` (Server/Client Components) |
| `views/partials/*.ejs` | `src/components/**/*.tsx` |
| `public/*` | `public/*` (–±–µ–Ј –Є–Ј–Љ–µ–љ–µ–љ–Є–є) |
